We’re introducing a new look for SeatGeek with a streamlined experience designed for iOS 11 and iPhone X.

We’ve made many improvements, focusing on helping you find the best deals to your favorite events, and showing you the view from your seat.

We’ve also been working on making the app more beautiful under the hood - including adding all features to iPad that iPhone users have so far been able to enjoy.

Thank you for installing SeatGeek, and letting us take you to the best events out there.
